Electrameccanica Vehicles Corp.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 10:43 AM ET
Automobiles

Company Overview of Electrameccanica Vehicles Corp.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Electrameccanica Vehicles Corp., a development-stage company, plans, develops, manufactures, and sells single person electric vehicles under the SOLO name. The company sells its products online through electrameccanica.com Website. Electrameccanica Vehicles Corp. was founded in 2015 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.


102 East 1st AvenueVancouver, BC V5T 1A4CanadaFounded in 201514 Employees



Phone: 604-428-7656

www.electrameccanica.com







