electrameccanica vehicles corp
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Automotive
Sub-Industry: Automobiles
Electrameccanica Vehicles Corp. manufactures automobiles. The Company develops electric vehicles with drive systems and dynamic induction charging for urban residents to commute. Electrameccanica Vehicles serves customers in Canada.




