Join the (r)Evolution




The Signature Series will be limited to the first 1,000 production SOLOs (MSRP of US$15,500). Each Signature Series SOLO receives an official tag signed by the Electra Meccanica design and development team, and includes the edition number and production date of your SOLO.





How You’re Changing the World
Electra Meccanica’s SOLO is the little something for everyone: an all electric, three-wheeled commuter vehicle made for the modern driver.

The single-seat cockpit is optimized to offer comfort and control to the approx. 90% of drivers travelling without passengers.
Get to work, hit the gym, pick up groceries: do all the things you need to, but more efficiently, by making the switch to electric.
With a range of approx. 100 miles on every charge, the SOLO tackles your average commute with range -and style- to spare.






